<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The 7 Habits of Highly Effective Job Seekers</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Merriweather:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
/* 1. CORE PRESENTATION SETUP */
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    display: grid;
    gap: 50px;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: 50px 0;
    place-items: center;
}

.slide-container {
    width: 1280px;
    height: 720px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 70px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

/* 1.1 RIT BRANDED DECORATION */
.slide-container::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 10px;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f76902; /* RIT Orange */
    z-index: 10;
}

.slide-container::after {
    content: 'RIT';
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    right: 40px;
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #f76902;
    opacity: 0.8;
}

.slide-container > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
}

/* 2. TYPOGRAPHY - ENLARGED FOR CLASSROOM VISIBILITY */
h1 {
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
    font-size: 90px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.slide-title {
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
    margin-bottom: 45px;
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
}

h3 {
    font-size: 42px;
    color: #f76902;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

p, li, td, th {
    font-size: 32px; /* Extra large font */
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #333;
}

.subtitle {
    font-size: 40px;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 25px;
}

/* 3. LAYOUT COMPONENTS */
.content-area {
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
}

.title-layout {
    text-align: center;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.two-column {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
}

.tiled-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    width: 100%;
}

.tile {
    flex: 1;
    background-color: #fcfcfc;
    padding: 50px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    text-align: center;
}

.tile .icon {
    font-size: 80px;
    color: #f76902;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    height: 420px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.image-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

/* SECTION TITLE (Used for Copyright) */
.section-title-layout {
    background-color: #000;
    margin: -70px;
    height: 720px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
}

.section-title-layout h2 {
    font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
    font-size: 80px;
    color: #fff;
}

/* TABLE STYLING */
table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
}

th {
    background-color: #000;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 36px;
}

td {
    padding: 30px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #f76902;
}

/* BLEED IMAGE LAYOUT */
.slide-container.bleed-image-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    padding: 0;
    align-items: start;
}

.bleed-image-layout .content-container {
    padding: 100px 70px;
}

.bleed-image-layout img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 720px;
    object-fit: cover;
}

/* HIGHLIGHT NUMBERS */
.big-number {
    font-size: 150px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f76902;
    line-height: 1;
}

/* BULLET LIST ICONS */
.styled-list {
    list-style: none;
}

.styled-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.styled-list li i {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 5px;
    color: #f76902;
    font-size: 32px;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Slide 1: Title Slide -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide1">
    <div class="title-layout">
        <h1>The 7 Habits</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">For First-Time Job Seekers</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 60px; border-top: 4px solid #f76902; padding-top: 20px; width: 400px;">
            <p style="font-weight: bold; color: #f76902;">Stephen Covey Applied</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 2: Habit 1 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide2">
    <h2 class="slide-title">1. Be Proactive</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="tiled-content">
            <div class="tile">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i></div>
                <h3>Take Initiative</h3>
                <p>Don't wait for a job. Find opportunities, follow up on apps, and ask for accommodations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tile">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt-lightning"></i></div>
                <h3>Choose Action</h3>
                <p>Take responsibility for your choices instead of blaming the market or others.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 3: Habit 2 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide3">
    <h2 class="slide-title">2. Begin with the End in Mind</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="two-column">
            <div>
                <h3>Have a Vision</h3>
                <p>Know what kind of career path you want.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Tailor your resume and elevator pitch to <strong>align</strong> with that specific goal.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <img src="http://googleusercontent.com/image_collection/image_retrieval/9435457736332748116" alt="Career roadmap vision">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 4: Habit 3 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide4">
    <h2 class="slide-title">3. Put First Things First</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>High Priority Task</th>
                    <th>Low Priority (Avoid)</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Resume Preparation</strong></td>
                    <td>Social Media Browsing</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Networking & Skills</strong></td>
                    <td>Busy-work tasks</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Interview Practice</strong></td>
                    <td>Procrastination</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 5: Habit 4 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide5">
    <h2 class="slide-title">4. Think Win-Win</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="two-column">
            <div class="image-wrapper" style="border-radius: 50%; height: 500px; width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <img src="http://googleusercontent.com/image_collection/image_retrieval/7689935257268134628" alt="Win-win collaboration">
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Mutual Benefit</h3>
                <p>In interviews, show how you help the company.</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 30px;">"Your skills help them succeed, and you grow professionally."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 6: Habit 5 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide6">
    <h2 class="slide-title">5. Understand, then be Understood</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="tiled-content">
            <div class="tile" style="border-top: 10px solid #000;">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-ear-listen"></i></div>
                <h3>Active Listening</h3>
                <p>Listen carefully to interview questions before you answer.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tile" style="border-top: 10px solid #f76902;">
                <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i></div>
                <h3>Expectations</h3>
                <p>Understand your manager's goals before starting a project.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 7: Habit 6 -->
<div class="slide-container bleed-image-layout" id="slide7">
    <div class="content-container">
        <h2 class="slide-title">6. Synergize</h2>
        <div class="content-area">
            <h3>Team Synergy</h3>
            <p>Value teamwork and diverse strengths. Collaboration is key to modern work.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Show employers you respect different perspectives and bring your own unique value.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
        <img src="http://googleusercontent.com/image_collection/image_retrieval/17351361875032741942" alt="Team synergy">
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 8: Habit 7 -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide8">
    <h2 class="slide-title">7. Sharpen the Saw</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <ul class="styled-list">
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> <strong>Constant Learning:</strong> Keep updating your skills with certifications and workshops.</li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-heart"></i> <strong>Health & Balance:</strong> Take care of your mental and physical health to perform your best.</li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-seedling"></i> <strong>Renewal:</strong> Rest is just as important as the job search itself.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 9: Summary -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide9">
    <h2 class="slide-title">Key Takeaways</h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="two-column">
            <div>
                <div class="big-number">1.</div>
                <p><strong>Initiative</strong>: Apply, follow up, and ask for access.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="big-number">2.</div>
                <p><strong>Focus</strong>: Know the kind of career you want.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
            <div class="big-number">3.</div>
            <p><strong>Growth</strong>: Keep learning and practicing resilience.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 10: Activity -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide10" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.8), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('http://googleusercontent.com/image_collection/image_retrieval/8410492849036487537'); background-size: cover; color: #fff;">
    <div class="title-layout">
        <h2 style="color: #f76902; font-size: 70px; margin-bottom: 30px;">In-Class Activity</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: bold;">"The Interview Dilemma"</p>
        <div style="text-align: left; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px;">
            <p style="color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong>Scenario:</strong> You are in an interview. The hiring manager seems confused about how to work with an interpreter.</p>
            <p style="color: #fff;"><strong>Task:</strong> Which 2 habits will you use to turn this into a "Win-Win"? Explain your steps to the class.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Slide 11: Copyright -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide11" style="padding: 0;">
    <div class="section-title-layout">
        <h2 style="font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px;">The 7 Habits for Job Seekers</h2>
        <p style="color: #f76902; font-weight: bold; font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 80px;">RIT | NCOM-207</p>
